@startuml
left to right direction
actor "Registered User" as user
actor "OpenRouteService" as api

rectangle "TourPlanner Backend" {
  usecase "POST /tours (Create Tour)" as UC1
  usecase "Calculate Route Metadata" as UC2
  usecase "Validate & Map RequestDTO" as UC3
  usecase "Handle Invalid Location" as UC4
  
  user --> UC1
  UC1 ..> UC3 : <<include>>
  UC3 ..> UC2 : <<include>>
  UC2 -- api
  UC2 ..> UC4 : <<extend>>
}

note right of UC4
  **Condition:** From/To locations 
  cannot be resolved by API
  **Response:** 422 Unprocessable Entity
end note
@enduml